headline: On Semiconductor Corporation (ON) Announces Revenue For The Second Quarter Of 2025
summary: On Semiconductor Corporation (NASDAQ:ON) is among the 11 Best Semiconductor Stocks with Huge Upside Potential. On Semiconductor Corporation (NASDAQ:ON) announced $1.47 billion in revenue for the second quarter of 2025, with 37.6% GAAP and non-GAAP gross margins.
